          "type": "text",
          "multiple": false,
          "values": [
            "Morning: Alfama & São Jorge Castle"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "body",
          "type": "text",
          "multiple": false,
          "values": [
            "Start before the crowds. Wind uphill through Alfama's tangled lanes to São Jorge Castle for the city's best panorama, then drift down past tiled facades and pause for a bica (espresso) at a tiny corner cafe."
          ]
        },
