        {
          "name": "body",
          "type": "text",
          "multiple": false,
          "values": [
            "As the lamps come on, settle into a small Alfama tavern for grilled sardines and a glass of vinho verde, then let live Fado — Lisbon's melancholy soul music — carry you into the night."
